'''Ocean Harvesters''' was a very successful agricultural corporation on the tropical resort world of [[Vaynai/Legends|Vaynai]]. The company harvested a wide variety of fish and other underwater agriculture using [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub]] harvesters.

